recommendation: A fault has occurred that may impact vehicle drivability. The issue relates to the nitrogen oxides sensor circuit range/performance. Monitor the vehicle for any unusual symptoms, such as reduced fuel efficiency or increased emissions. We recommend checking the vehicle at the next convenient stop and scheduling a diagnostic check with a professional mechanic to address the sensor issue and ensure the emissions system is functioning properly.
effectOnComponent: Decreased engine performance (reduced power and acceleration). The vehicle may struggle to accelerate, especially when going uphill or when loaded. The vehicle may also idle rough.
